        96.0,
        166.96,
        208.17,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p102_s0010",
      "text": "Payload: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        140.41,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p102_s0011",
      "text": "The Payload of the request contains a list of the Nx_Ports for which the Alias_ID is to be",
      "bbox": [
        140.4,
        190.96,
        539.99,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p102_s0012",
      "text": "recognized and the Alias_ID to be recognized as an Alias_ID.  The format of the Payload is shown in",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        539.86,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p102_s0013",
      "text": "table 81.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        134.36,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
